it from news reports he said chemotherapy could probably have kept 
the patient alive for two years 
i think he died because of media hype bihari said hed 
be alive and stable now with conservative treatment 
however alonso said he had advised the patient against 
hyperthermia but that bihari had insisted that the patient receive 
it 
