of human rights which have occurred in these years of war 
especially with the military bombing of rural zones 
the peace talks in san jose costa ricas capital were expected 
to focus on rebel demands that the size of the armed forces 
estimated at 54000 men be reduced and that officers guilty of 
severe human rights violations be purged 
