the satellite would be carried aboard the space shuttle 
discovery tentatively scheduled to be launched in early october 
antinuclear and peace groups fear an explosion at the launch 
pad or in the air could scatter deadly radioactivity over florida 
protests are planned closer to the launch date 
theyre entitled to their viewpoint i happen to think theyre 
wrong said derek eaton the european space agencys project 
manager for the satellite known as ulysses 
reports predicting devastation in the event of an accident are 
