enormous solar panels that would be required officials said 
white house approval of discoverys launch with ulysses is 
expected by midseptember such clearance is necessary when rtgs 
are used 
nasa wants to launch the discovery oct 5 the space agency has 
until oct 23 to get the shuttle off the ground during the correct 
alignment of earth the sun and jupiter whose gravitational field 
will slingshot ulysses back to the sun 
if discovery fails to lift off by then the mission must be 
delayed 13 months 
the 750 million ulysses mission will span five years the 
spacecraft would be the first to orbit over the suns poles 
providing important information about the interaction between the 
sun and earth 
nasas share of the mission is an estimated 500 million the 
european space agency paid for the 250 million cost of the 
spacecraft 
