continued to increase its armed forces in kuwait he said 
intelligence estimates now put the number at 160000 
he said there has been no major change in the character of the 
iraqi forces which the pentagon earlier described as having a 
defensive appearance 
theres a continuing flow in and out of kuwait he said 
